&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;ImagingAppointment Facilitator - Band 3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Imaging Department&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required to work cross-site at Ashford and St Peter’s Hospitals.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;37.5 hours per week&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an appointments facilitator to join the team in the Imaging Department at St Peter’s Hospital. The successful candidates will be proficient in customer service, will have excellent telephone skills and a good level of IT skills. They will be required to work on the reception, answer the phone and book Imaging appointments within the department. They must be a team player, able to work independently using their own initiative and have good communication skills. The successful candidates need to be able to commit to flexible working hours and some unsocial working may be required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
